{{Quote|Warool noggaggllo?|[[Utai/Legends|Utai]] dragonmount wrangler to [[Obi-Wan Kenobi/Legends|Obi-Wan Kenobi]]|<ref name="RotSn">[[Star Wars: Revenge of the Sith (novelization)|''Star Wars: Revenge of the Sith'' novelization]]</ref>}}
This '''language''' was the native tongue of the [[Utai/Legends|Utai]] on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Utapau/Legends|Utapau]]. The Utai appeared to speak this language exclusively, though most [[Pau'an/Legends|Pau'ans]] spoke both [[Galactic Basic Standard/Legends|Basic]] and [[Utapese/Legends|Utapese]].

This language was characterized as a series of "burbling glottal hoots", as [[Obi-Wan Kenobi/Legends|Obi-Wan Kenobi]] observed while attempting to communicate with an Utai [[Varactyl/Legends|varactyl]] wrangler in [[Pau City/Legends|Pau City]].<ref name="RotSn" />

